{p} {p}
Your request for exclusion should set forth your name, address and
telephone number. All requests for exclusion must be signed by or on
behalf of the person requesting exclusion. IF A REQUEST FOR EXCLUSION
DOES NOT INCLUDE ALL OF THE FOREGOING INFORMATION, IT SHALL NOT BE A
VALID REQUEST FOR EXCLUSION AND THE PERSON FILING THE INVALID REQUEST
FOR EXCLUSION SHALL BE DEEMED A SETTLEMENT CLASS MEMBER IF FINAL
CERTIFICATION OF THE SETTLEMENT CLASS AND THE SETTLEMENT IS APPROVED.
{p} {p}
If your request for exclusion is timely received, the Court will
exclude you from the Settlement Class and you will not be bound by
the Settlement described above. You cannot participate in the
Settlement, but can proceed with your claims individually. If you do
not request exclusion, you will be entitled to participate in the
Settlement and your interests will be represented by:
