 VI. EXAMINATION OF PAPERS AND INQUIRIES
{p} {p}
The above is only a summary of the terms of the proposed Settlement.
For a more detailed statement of the matters involved in the Action,
reference is made to the Complaint, the other pleadings, the
Settlement Agreement submitted to the Court, orders entered by the
Court and other papers filed in the Action, which may be inspected at
the Office of the Clerk, Circuit Court of Cook County, Chancery
Division, State of Illinois, during business hours each business day.
{p} {p}
ALL QUESTIONS RELATING TO THE PROPOSED SETTLEMENT SHOULD BE DIRECTED
TO CLASS COUNSEL. PLEASE DO NOT CONTACT THE COURT OR THE CLERK'S
OFFICE FOR INFORMATION.
